"estudiantes de la Unidad Educativa Fiscomisional La Dolorosa. Nos complace "
"darles la bienvenida a este espacio digital creado con el propósito de "
"rescatar, preservar y difundir la historia musical lojana."
msgstr ""
"students of the La Dolorosa Fiscomisional Educational Unit. We are pleased "
"to welcome you to this digital space created with the purpose of rescuing, "
"preserving, and disseminating Loja's musical history."

