msgid ""
"La creación de una página web dedicada al Rescate Digital de la Historia "
"Musical Lojana surge de la necesidad de preservar, difundir y revalorizar el"
" patrimonio cultural de Loja, reconocido como uno de los principales "
"referentes musicales del Ecuador."
msgstr ""
"The creation of a website dedicated to the Digital Rescue of Loja's Musical "
"History arises from the need to preserve, disseminate, and revalue the "
"cultural heritage of Loja, recognized as one of the main musical references "
"in Ecuador."

