msgid ""
"Loja es reconocida a nivel sudamericano por exportar grandes talentos "
"históricos en el ámbito de la música sacra y académica."
msgstr ""
"Loja is recognized at the South American level for exporting great "
"historical talents in the field of sacred and academic music."

